llm_commentary: [Kick Off] The Round of 16 begins! Austria faces Turkey, both eager to advance.
[Goal] Goal! Austria 0, Turkey 1. Merih Demiral heads in from the corner delivery.
[General] Austria dominating the early exchanges, controlling 100% possession in midfield.
[Shot Missed] Attempt missed! Christoph Baumgartner dribbles past his man but fires wide from the edge of the box.
[General] Austria dominating early with 91% possession, Seiwald heavily involved in midfield play.
[Injury] Early concern for Austria as Christoph Baumgartner goes down with an injury.
[Shot Missed] Lienhart's header from the six-yard box goes over the bar. Austria pushing forward.

[General] Turkey controlling the midfield with 54% possession, Demiral highly active early on.
